&lt;p&gt;At Asana we’re looking for curious, collaborative, and creative students to join our 12-week summer Product Design internship program. This program focuses on bringing students currently studying at a college or university into our Design team to develop and work on complex and challenging problems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;During this internship, you’ll work directly with dedicated Design mentors who are trained and motivated to ensure your success. You’ll also have the opportunity to work with Engineering, User Research, Product Management, Data Science, and the rest of our amazing Design crew to ship experiences that make it as simple as possible for teams big and small to realize the value of Asana.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This internship is based in our &lt;strong&gt;Warsaw&lt;/strong&gt; office with an office-centric hybrid schedule. Along with most Asanas, you’ll work from this office in person on Mondays, Tuesdays, and Thursdays. Most Asanas have the option to work from home on Wednesdays and Fridays. If you&#39;re interviewing for this role, your Talent Acquisition Partner will share more about the in-office requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the design team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;We design the future of teamwork.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;Asana has a bold, ambitious mission: help humanity thrive by enabling the world’s teams to work together effortlessly. Our design team is at the heart of that mission.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Asana Design is an inclusive and collaborative community. We’re a diverse group of designers from different backgrounds &lt;em&gt;(product, brand and content design, design operations, producers, motion design, film, copywriting)&lt;/em&gt;. We are a team that loves combining research, data insights, and peer feedback into a human-centered design process to produce designs that are core to the power of our applications. We partner with people across Asana to create our product, shape our brand, and drive greater impact through design. We use design to solve challenges and create experiences that customers love. We also take the time to get weird and have fun along the way.We believe every designer should have the opportunity to grow and learn by utilizing their strengths and nurturing their interests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our employees in Poland are employed under a contract of employment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll achieve&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pair with our experienced designers, who will significantly enhance your collaboration skills and grow your ability to identify and transform complex problems into intuitive, human-centered solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be actively involved in the end-to-end design process by exploring concepts, ideating on solutions in jams, and creating eng-ready final designs in Figma&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to everything from broad strategic discussions to the specifics of a component interaction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work across the organization to ship experiences that are cohesive within the broader Asana product experience, ensuring your design scales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with seasoned designers to learn new methodologies for divergent thinking and understand its impact on end users&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work under the direction of a design mentor, while collaborating with cross functional partners to identify problems, set strategy, establish vision, ship projects, and gather insights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience career growth and personal development with world-class mentorship and development programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Currently enrolled in a degree program in a design-related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Anticipated graduation date between December 2026 and July 2027&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Portfolio with a solid foundation in human-centered design practices that showcases strong interaction and interface design skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to express ideas via rich stories and prototypes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Aptitude to come up with novel, simple solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to think systematically and work through challenging problems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for creating a high-quality user experience, down to those little details that matter&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Figma or similar design tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong collaboration and communication skills, curiosity, and eagerness to learn and grow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excited to be a part of an inclusive culture where everyone brings their whole selves to work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates curiosity about AI tools and emerging technologies, with a willingness to learn and leverage them to enhance productivity, collaboration, or decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Asana, we&#39;re committed to building teams that include a variety of backgrounds, perspectives, and skills, as this is critical to helping us achieve our mission. If you&#39;re interested in this role and don&#39;t meet every listed requirement, we still encourage you to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we’ll offer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generous, transparent and fair compensation system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MacBooks with all necessary accessories&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meals reimbursement on the days that you work from the office&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our comprehensive compensation package plays a big part in how we recognize you for the impact you have on our path to achieving our mission. We believe that compensation should be reflective of the value you create relative to the market value of your role. To ensure pay is fair and not impacted by biases, we&#39;re committed to looking at market value which is why we check ourselves and conduct a yearly pay equity audit.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Talent Acquisition Partner will share more on the estimated pay rate. The actual hourly rate will vary based on various factors, including market and individual qualifications objectively assessed during the interview process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#LI-Hybrid #internship&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-pm-slice=&quot;1 1 []&quot;&gt;Asana is a leading platform for human + AI collaboration. Millions of teams around the world rely on Asana to achieve their most important goals, faster. Asana has been named to Fortune&#39;s Best Workplaces for 7+ years and recognized by Fast Company, Forbes, and Gartner for excellence in workplace culture and innovation. We offer an exceptional office-centric culture while adopting the best elements of hybrid models to ensure that every one of our global team members can work together effortlessly. With 13+ offices all over the world, we are always looking for individuals who care about building technology that drives positive change in the world and a culture where everyone feels that they belong.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-pm-slice=&quot;1 1 []&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;LinkThemeablePresentation LinkPrimaryPresentation LinkPrimaryPresentation--sentimentSelected PrimaryLink HighlightSol HighlightSol--core HighlightSol--buildingBlock&quot; href=&quot;https://www.gem.com/form?formID=fbcdec8c-3442-43b9-9b45-d2b5f4ea25db&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Join Asana’s Talent Network&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to stay up to date on job opportunities and life at Asana.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-root=&quot;1&quot;&gt;RDQ227R1172&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Databricks, we are passionate about helping data teams solve the world&#39;s toughest problems — from making the next mode of transportation a reality to accelerating the development of medical breakthroughs. We do this by building and running the world&#39;s best data and AI infrastructure platform so our customers can use deep data insights to improve their business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Product Pricing &amp;amp; Commercialization Intern, you will join our world-class Commercialization team to help shape the monetization strategies that power Databricks’ hyper-growth. During your 12-week internship, you’ll lead high-impact projects—from designing pricing for new AI innovations to optimizing our global commercial frameworks—with opportunities for full-time employment within the team the following year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Throughout the internship, you will be mentored by a dedicated sponsor and have the opportunity to connect with senior leaders across the organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Impact you will have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Strategic Projects:&lt;/strong&gt; Own a high-priority monetization project from data-driven research to recommendation, such as defining the pricing for a new feature,evaluating a new market segment, and understanding competitor pricing models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Inform High-Stakes Decisions:&lt;/strong&gt; Provide the analytical rigor,data-driven insights, and first-principles thinking that shape commercial thinking for product areas with significant revenue potential.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communicate with Clarity:&lt;/strong&gt; Author insightful documents (e.g., internal strategy papers or Business Requirements Documents) that synthesize complex ideas for both technical and executive audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enable the Field:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate on creating product documentation and sales enablement content to ensure our field teams can effectively communicate Databricks’ value to customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Influence the Roadmap:&lt;/strong&gt; Work across the Pricing and Product teams to understand the cross-portfolio consequences of pricing decisions, ensuring alignment across the product platform and CSP partnerships (AWS, Azure, GCP).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will graduate from an MBA program in Spring 2027.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have 3-5 years of previous professional experience in management consulting, investment banking, strategy, operations, business analysis, or related fields.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You demonstrate an advanced ability to define and break down ambiguous and complex business problems with limited guidance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are an excellent communicator (both written and oral), with the ability to synthesize complex information into clear, insightful takeaways and action-oriented recommendations.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You put the team before yourself and are willing to get hands-on, no matter how small the task&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience in enterprise software and cloud platforms preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience with SQL preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay Range Transparency&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Databricks is committed to fair and equitable compensation practices. The pay range(s) for this role is listed below and represents the expected salary range for non-commissionable roles or on-target earnings for commissionable roles.&amp;nbsp; Actual compensation packages are based on several factors that are unique to each candidate, including but not limited to job-related skills, depth of experience, relevant certifications and training, and specific work location. Based on the factors above, Databricks anticipates utilizing the full width of the range. The total compensation package for this position may also include eligibility for annual performance bonus, equity, and the benefits listed above. For more information regarding which range your location is in visit our page &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.databricks.com/sites/default/files/2024-08/us-pay-zone-mapping.pdf&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;SF Bay Area Hourly Rate&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$40&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$40 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Databricks&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Databricks is the data and AI company. More than 10,000 organizations worldwide — including Comcast, Condé Nast, Grammarly, and over 50% of the Fortune 500 — rely on the Databricks Data Intelligence Platform to unify and democratize data, analytics and AI. Databricks is headquartered in San Francisco, with offices around the globe and was founded by the original creators of Lakehouse, Apache Spark™, Delta Lake and MLflow. To learn more, follow Databricks on&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 54, 33);&quot;&gt;&lt;a style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 54, 33);&quot; href=&quot;https://twitter.com/databricks&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/databricks&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1700237575733000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw03FL8fJvOD97ytN02f5G2C&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 54, 33);&quot; href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/databricks&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/company/databricks&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1700237575733000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw15dLk3q8VxTfHEgCUg7NSt&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;and&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 54, 33);&quot; href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/databricksinc&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.facebook.com/databricksinc&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1700237575733000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw39EcncitnlqV72EG2-RqXJ&quot;&gt;Facebook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;At Databricks, we strive to provide comprehensive benefits and perks that meet the needs of all of our employees. For specific details on the benefits offered in your region, please visit&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mybenefitsnow.com/databricks&quot;&gt;https://www.mybenefitsnow.com/databricks&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Commitment to Diversity and Inclusion&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Databricks, we are committed to fostering a diverse and inclusive culture where everyone can excel. We take great care to ensure that our hiring practices are inclusive and meet equal employment opportunity standards. Individuals looking for employment at Databricks are considered without regard to age, color, disability, ethnicity, family or marital status, gender identity or expression, language, national origin, physical and mental ability, political affiliation, race, religion, sexual orientation, socio-economic status, veteran status, and other protected characteristics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compliance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;If access to export-controlled technology or source code is required for performance of job duties, it is within Employer&#39;s discretion whether to apply for a U.S. government license for such positions, and Employer may decline to proceed with an applicant on this basis alone.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GAQ227R116&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Databricks, we are passionate about helping data teams solve the world&#39;s toughest problems - from making the next mode of transportation a reality to accelerating the development of medical breakthroughs. We do this by building and running the world&#39;s best data and AI infrastructure platform so our customers can use deep data insights to improve their business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a People Analytics MBA intern, you’ll drive insights and impact across our People (HR) function and all of Databricks. During your 12 week internship, you&#39;ll work on impactful projects that drive decisions about how we hire, train, enable, assess, and coach Bricksters - and more. You’ll apply a current-state lens to People processes as they exist today while helping to transform our future. Successful interns may have opportunities for full-time employment in the following year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Throughout the internship, you’ll be mentored by a dedicated sponsor and have the opportunity to connect with senior leaders across the organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Impact You’ll Have:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Execution:&lt;/strong&gt; Own the end-to-end outcome for at least one major team-wide initiative (e.g., optimizing a specific People practice or workstream) from data gathering to executive recommendation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Excellence:&lt;/strong&gt; Develop and enhance our data foundation by building advanced BI dashboards, AI-first conversational interactions, and automated solutions that are scalable and maintainable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SME Partnership:&lt;/strong&gt; Act as a thought partner to company leaders, translating workforce intelligence into actionable insights that will impact the performance of all Bricksters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advanced Analytics:&lt;/strong&gt; Execute complex analysis - including basic forecasting using time-series data - to predict trends in hiring, retention, or employee engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Communication:&lt;/strong&gt; Convert recurring analysis requests into self-service tools, enabling leaders to make data-driven decisions independently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education:&lt;/strong&gt; Currently pursuing an MBA with a graduation date in Spring 2027.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; 3–5 years of professional experience in Business Intelligence, People Analytics, Management Consulting, or a highly analytical operations role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Skills:&lt;/strong&gt; You have advanced skills in BI tools (e.g., Tableau, PowerBI) and a strong grasp of SQL. You understand how systems relate to business processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ambiguity Navigator:&lt;/strong&gt; You can recognize and effectively navigate ambiguity with limited direction, turning &quot;messy&quot; data into a clear narrative.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Acumen:&lt;/strong&gt; You can identify data gaps in operational processes and propose solutions to close them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clear Communicator: &lt;/strong&gt;You are an excellent communicator, with an ability to synthesize complex information into clear, insightful takeaways and action-oriented recommendations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Culture Champion:&lt;/strong&gt; You are ready to collaborate closely with colleagues and network across functional areas to foster Databricks&#39; cultural values.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay Range Transparency&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Databricks is committed to fair and equitable compensation practices. The pay range(s) for this role is listed below and represents the expected salary range for non-commissionable roles or on-target earnings for commissionable roles.&amp;nbsp; Actual compensation packages are based on several factors that are unique to each candidate, including but not limited to job-related skills, depth of experience, relevant certifications and training, and specific work location. Based on the factors above, Databricks anticipates utilizing the full width of the range. The total compensation package for this position may also include eligibility for annual performance bonus, equity, and the benefits listed above. For more information regarding which range your location is in visit our page &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.databricks.com/sites/default/files/2024-08/us-pay-zone-mapping.pdf&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;SF Bay Area Hourly Rate&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$40&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$40 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Databricks&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Databricks is the data and AI company. More than 10,000 organizations worldwide — including Comcast, Condé Nast, Grammarly, and over 50% of the Fortune 500 — rely on the Databricks Data Intelligence Platform to unify and democratize data, analytics and AI. Databricks is headquartered in San Francisco, with offices around the globe and was founded by the original creators of Lakehouse, Apache Spark™, Delta Lake and MLflow. To learn more, follow Databricks on&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 54, 33);&quot;&gt;&lt;a style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 54, 33);&quot; href=&quot;https://twitter.com/databricks&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/databricks&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1700237575733000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw03FL8fJvOD97ytN02f5G2C&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 54, 33);&quot; href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/databricks&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/company/databricks&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1700237575733000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw15dLk3q8VxTfHEgCUg7NSt&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;and&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 54, 33);&quot; href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/databricksinc&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.facebook.com/databricksinc&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1700237575733000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw39EcncitnlqV72EG2-RqXJ&quot;&gt;Facebook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;At Databricks, we strive to provide comprehensive benefits and perks that meet the needs of all of our employees. For specific details on the benefits offered in your region, please visit&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mybenefitsnow.com/databricks&quot;&gt;https://www.mybenefitsnow.com/databricks&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Commitment to Diversity and Inclusion&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Databricks, we are committed to fostering a diverse and inclusive culture where everyone can excel. We take great care to ensure that our hiring practices are inclusive and meet equal employment opportunity standards. Individuals looking for employment at Databricks are considered without regard to age, color, disability, ethnicity, family or marital status, gender identity or expression, language, national origin, physical and mental ability, political affiliation, race, religion, sexual orientation, socio-economic status, veteran status, and other protected characteristics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compliance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;If access to export-controlled technology or source code is required for performance of job duties, it is within Employer&#39;s discretion whether to apply for a U.S. government license for such positions, and Employer may decline to proceed with an applicant on this basis alone.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;At Databricks, we are passionate about helping data teams solve the world&#39;s toughest problems — from making the next mode of transportation a reality to accelerating the development of medical breakthroughs. We do this by building and running the world&#39;s best data and AI infrastructure platform so our customers can use deep data insights to improve their business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Strategic Finance MBA Intern, you will join our world-class finance team to drive insights and impact across Databricks. During your 12 week internship, you&#39;ll work on impactful strategic finance projects,. Your work will provide valuable insights to leadership, helping drive data-driven decisions. Successful interns may have opportunities for full-time employment in these functions the following year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Throughout the internship, you will be mentored by a dedicated sponsor and have the opportunity to connect with senior leaders across the organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Impact you will have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and enhance our data and reporting foundation, implementing cutting-edge dashboards and tools that provide visibility into key operating metrics and improve business performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present findings to senior leadership within both Finance, Sales, and Product, highlighting key trends and translating financial insights into actionable decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solve complex problems analytically, gathering and summarizing large datasets to drive efficient executive decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Find creative solutions for data challenges and translate complex analyses into clear, easy-to-understand narratives and presentations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with team members and stakeholders across multiple functions including Sales, Product, Engineering, Finance, and Data Science&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build an understanding of enterprise software business problems while developing career-relevant skills using Databricks products and modern analytics tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will graduate in Spring 2027 from an MBA program.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have 3-5 years of previous professional experience in management consulting, investment banking, strategy, operations, business analysis, or related fields.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You demonstrate an advanced ability to define and break down ambiguous and complex business problems with limited guidance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are an excellent communicator (written and oral), with an ability to synthesize complex information into clear, insightful takeaways and action-oriented recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are adept at using technology to streamline / optimize business deliverables&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
