&lt;li&gt;Analytically and problem-solving &amp;nbsp; minded,&amp;nbsp; detail and results oriented, and a quick learner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to present in front of others and give presentations.&lt;/li&gt;
