&lt;p&gt;Our interns have the opportunity to build a strong community - with their fellow interns, within their teams, and with the broader company. We want you to grow professionally and you’ll do that through participating in events like our Executive Speaker Series and Brown Bags.&amp;nbsp; And of course, we want you to have fun too.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;What you can look forward to as a Full-Time Okta employee!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
