&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an individual to join the Global Partner Marketing team, a dynamic group responsible for developing and executing joint marketing programs with Okta&#39;s most strategic partners. You will work closely with Partner Marketing Managers to create and manage initiatives that drive engagement, build pipeline, and have a measurable impact on Okta&#39;s business objectives through our global partner ecosystem. This cross-functional role involves working alongside teams in sales, marketing, and partner alliances.&lt;/p&gt;
