&lt;li&gt;Support the Global Partner Marketing team with the planning, execution, and measurement of joint marketing programs and campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gain a deep understanding of Okta’s joint value proposition with various partner types (Global System Integrations, Cloud Service Providers, Technology Partners) to assist with developing joint marketing and sales content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate and collaborate with Partner Marketing Managers and internal sales teams across different time zones&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and report on the performance of partner marketing campaigns, measuring key performance indicators (KPIs) to assess effectiveness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Liaise with external agencies and design teams&lt;/li&gt;
