&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will graduate between fall 2026 and Summer 2027 with a degree in Computer Science, Engineering, or related subject&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have implementation skills with a general purpose program language, such as Python, Java, or C++&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have good knowledge of algorithms, data structures, and OOP principles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are excited to solve ambiguous problems with a collaborative team&lt;/li&gt;
