&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ready to be pushed beyond what you think you’re capable of?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Coinbase, our mission is to increase economic freedom in the world. It’s a massive, ambitious opportunity that demands the best of us, every day, as we build the emerging onchain platform — and with it, the future global financial system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To achieve our mission, we’re seeking a very specific candidate. We want someone who is passionate about our mission and who believes in the power of crypto and blockchain technology to update the financial system. We want someone who is eager to leave their mark on the world, who relishes the pressure and privilege of working with high caliber colleagues, and who actively seeks feedback to keep leveling up. We want someone who will run towards, not away from, solving the company’s hardest problems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/mission&quot;&gt;work culture&lt;/a&gt; is intense and isn’t for everyone. But if you want to build the future alongside others who excel in their disciplines and expect the same from you, there’s no better place to be.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While many roles at Coinbase are remote-first, we are not remote-only. In-person participation is required throughout the year. Team and company-wide offsites are held multiple times annually to foster collaboration, connection, and alignment. Attendance is expected and fully supported.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is a 12-week internship during summer 2026.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Tax Information Reporting intern will be an integral part of the Coinbase Tax team supporting the day to day operations of the global tax information reporting and withholding function. This role will primarily focus on domestic and international global tax information reporting and withholding and collaborate in all aspects of Coinbase’s compliance with these requirements. The candidate also will work closely with the broader Coinbase product, platform and data functions and help drive initiatives for continuous process improvements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Coinbase Tax team ensures that Coinbase complies fully with its tax obligations in all of the jurisdictions in which Coinbase operates. This includes building a world class set of tax protocols adapted for the holding, purchase, sale and trading of digital assets. We are passionate about tax and crypto, and we are looking for an ideal candidate with a similar passion and collaborative focus to join our world class team!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing (ie. job duties):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform quality assurance testing on data to ensure accuracy and determine if there are gaps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Estimate form and transaction volumes for our IRS 1099-DA filings and print and production estimates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate on AI-driven initiatives to streamline operational workflows and enhance customer inquiry responses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present your completed project to managers, team guides, and leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for in you (ie. job requirements):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excel or Google Sheets experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written and verbal communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outstanding detail-orientation and process-orientation skills&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborative and positive orientation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to pivot and learn&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Currently pursuing a degree or certificate in finance, accounting, business administration or a related discipline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic knowledge of SQL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with Snowflake, Looker or similar analytic tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job #: &lt;span data-sheets-root=&quot;1&quot;&gt;P73545&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
